      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STILTON QUINN (4) goes very well at this journey having never missed the frame including two wins and two placings. In the money last time at this track (22.51) in a Grade 5, finishing a 2 length third. Looks a leading chance on best. BLURRY (1) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Nowra over 365m behind Ashby Cola (21.55) in a Grade 5. The form out of his last race has been franked. Should be thereabouts. MORE RAIN (3) caught the eye when posting a sharp 22.83 over 400m at The Gardens three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Top win three back and rates a key player again. IN THE QUEUE (2) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
